'''''Benet's Reader's Encyclopedia of American Literature''''' was published in 1991 by [[Harper Collins Publishers]]. The book contains facts on American authors' major and lesser works, summarizes the critical consensus, gives biographical information and often lists secondary [[biography|biographical]] and critical works.

