==Unique features==
<!-- Please do not add new entries to this table unless there is a Wikipedia article about the product. Thank you. -->
{| class="wikitable sortable" style="text-align:left; display:block; border:1px; overflow-x:auto; padding-bottom:1px;"
|+ Unique features in webmail products
|-
! scope="col" | Name
! scope="col" | Features
|-
! style="text-align:left;" | [[FastMail]]
| One time passwords;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fastmail.com/help/account/alternatelogin.html |title=Alternative logins |publisher=FastMail}}</ref> spam filter; backscatter detection;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fastmail.com/help/technical/backscatter.html |title=Backscatter |publisher=FastMail}}</ref> deletion of selected attachments. Android and IPhone apps.
|-
! style="text-align:left;" | [[Gmail]]
| Account verification via SMS or voice call in some countries;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/114129 |title=Frequently Asked Questions on Account Verification via SMS or voice call}}</ref> Messages grouped into "conversations"; "Normal" view via Settings; Labels instead of folders; Undo send (implemented as a delayed send)
